<h5 id="subject_1129298">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;topic=59876.msg1129298#msg1129298" rel="nofollow">Re: 【第八章】背景特性（Traits）</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1129298'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1129298'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #11 于:</strong> 2021-08-13, 周五 15:57:47 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1129298_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1129298">刻印使（Birthmark）：你出生时便携带着某种特殊胎记，其形状恰似你日后所信奉神祗的圣徽。此胎记可以在你施法时作为<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">圣法器</span>使用，同时也是你的信仰的肉体具现、增添了你对神祗的虔敬之心——你在对抗魅惑和胁迫效果的<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">意志豁免</span>中获得+2背景加值。<br><br><a href="https://aonprd.com/TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Birthmark" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">https://aonprd.com/TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Birthmark</a><br><br>Birthmark<br>Source Ultimate Campaign pg. 54, Second Darkness Player&#039;s Guide pg. 12, Advanced Player&#039;s Guide pg. 1<br>Category Basic (Faith)<br>You were born with a strange birthmark that looks very similar to the holy symbol of the god you chose to worship later in life. This birthmark can serve you as a divine focus for casting spells, and as a physical manifestation of your faith, and it increases your devotion to your god. You gain a +2 trait bonus on<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"> all saving throws against charm and compulsion effects.</span><br><br>圣法器=圣徽<br>不只是意志豁免，是所以豁免（虽然不知怎么存在别的豁免，但的确有机会…吧？）</div>
</div>
</div>
